did.head: Descriptive Summary
did.repository: Special Collections, University of Virginia Library
did.physdesc: This collection consists of ca. 136,800 items.

accessrestrict.head: Access Restrictions
accessrestrict.p: Stored off-site. Users must request boxes 48 hours in advance of desired use. Neither drop-in nor next-day requests can be fulfilled. For additional information, contact Special Collections.

userestrict.head: Use Restrictions
userestrict.p:
See the
University of Virginia Library’s use policy.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Gitchell's Studio Collection, 1969-1989, Accession #11567, Special Collections, University of Virginia Library, Charlottesville, Va.

acqinfo.head: Acquisition Information
acqinfo.p: This collection was a gift to the Library from Jim Carpenter of Gitchell's Studio on December 14, 1999.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Content Information
scopecontent.p: The collection consists chiefly of studio portraits of individuals and some groups, along with both formal and casual wedding photographs.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: Negatives and proofs are arranged in two chronological groups, Weddings and Portraits. Within each year, items are sorted (but not arranged) alphabetically by the last name of the subject; wedding photographs are under the bride's last name.
